sources.title: Outlaw Action | Days of Jesse James 1939 | Crooked Bankers Vs Legendary Lawmen of the Wild West
sources.description:
Roy Rogers hunts the infamous Jesse James, finding himself on the wrong side of the badge to outrun the law hot on Jesse's trail. With Gabby Whittaker telling tall tales, and Captain Worthington closing in, Roy must unmask the real villain before the posse catches the wrong outlaw.

Directed by Joseph Kane

Main cast:
Roy Rogers - Roy Rogers
George 'Gabby' Hayes - Gabby Whittaker
Don 'Red' Barry - Jesse James
Pauline Moore - Mary Whittaker
Harry Woods - Captain Worthington
Arthur Loft - Sam Wyatt

Genres: Western, Drama, Music, Romance
Release date: December 20, 1939

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/qmTdWOmhEl0
